{"tid":17521,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡利奧斯︰爭英超冠軍唔使預曼聯","createTime":"2016-12-02T00:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T14:15:56.000Z","uid":7715,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"921b06221bf98cf7d02991c1e647182f78c344e2","tid":17521,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:41:50.000Z","msg":"利物浦門將卡利奧斯認為，今季英超冠軍將是紅軍、曼城、車路士及阿仙奴之爭，言下之意曼聯及熱刺將不在他的爭標之列。<br />\n<br />\n英超聯賽榜現時形勢緊湊，前4名只有3分之差，當被問到今季爭標球隊時，卡利奧斯說︰「車路士、曼城、阿仙奴和我們，很多人認為曼城有哥迪奧拿帶領會是冠軍熱門，車路士亦正值顛峰狀態。」<br />\n<br />\n他補充說︰「我們距離目標仍有很長路要走，球隊仍未贏得甚麼，或許大家會認為若利物浦最終只是第二名亦是失望而回，但我們的首要目標是下季重返歐聯賽事。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=N9koirI5nbtQ%2BujBUnukppkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c388ffae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"aa8f6ef32420407911feb2e1c861a725917f65e7","tid":17521,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babfcd735e63aa2f17fc376375f8ed61ceea106a","tid":17521,"uid":12027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:50:32.000Z","msg":"你留係度定返高登"},{"pid":"a80e542cfa6e93bf421d5e96f4d5d50545b22174","tid":17521,"uid":2676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:51:11.000Z","msg":"祝返高登者死全家"},{"pid":"abdbb288881b2b9cf60ebde1ea3f21a3e56c81b3","tid":17521,"uid":277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:51:38.000Z","msg":"Book 場"},{"pid":"a66d06de840a9f31a5f4079c8140743dba8e9031","tid":17521,"uid":18663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:51:41.000Z","msg":"唔洗佢講我都知獌冇機啦！"},{"pid":"a7d1b99c73cf431e0288ecf8e826b65ef1c3ab73","tid":17521,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你留係度定返高登</blockquote><br />\n不了 joe仔而家仲柒過當爺"},{"pid":"f1505f2bcae4d95f82ac2c4f77ebc89607e55